  <h1 class="app-header">Privilege Walk‚Äç</h1>
  {{#unless hasBegun}}
  <p>
    A Privilege Walk demonstrates the ways society privileges certain individuals over others.
  </p>
  <p>
    On the following pages you will be asked a question. Based on your life experience, you can click to either take a step forwards or backwards. At the end you'll receive a score which you can use to compare your privilege with others.
  </p>
  <div>
    <button {{action "handleBegin"}} class="begin-button">Let's begin!</button>
  </div>
  {{else}}
  <QuestionContainer
  @currentIndex={{currentIndex}}
  @score={{score}}
  @isLastQuestion={{isLastQuestion}}
  @isDone={{isDone}}
  @startOver={{action "startOver"}}
  @saveAnswers={{action saveAnswers}}
  @model={{model}}
  />
  {{/unless}}
